                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-551" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SPRAGG</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a carrier, of Clapham, and am the prisoner's brother. On 16th March I saw him near St. George's Church, Borough—he gave me 14<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 7<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and said he had received it from Mr. Pope to pay away in the City, and he had not done so, but had been drinking, and lost the remainder—he told me to give it to Mr. Pope, as he did not like to take it himself.</p>
